task.action:
In `src/app/globals.css`, add the following under `@layer utilities` (create it if it doesn't exist). This pattern is based on Material Design dark theme guidelines and fintech industry standards (Mercury, Stripe): Surface lightening for elevation, 200ms ease transitions, :focus-visible for keyboard accessibility, and prefers-reduced-motion support for the transform.

```css
@layer utilities {
  .interactive-card {
    transition: background-color 200ms ease, border-color 200ms ease;
  }
  .interactive-card:hover,
  .interactive-card:focus-visible {
    background-color: var(--color-secondary-800);
    border-color: oklch(1 0 0 / 8%);
  }
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
  .interactive-card {
    transition: background-color 200ms ease, border-color 200ms ease, transform 200ms ease;
  }
  .interactive-card:hover,
  .interactive-card:focus-visible {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
}
```

Do NOT use `box-shadow` animation, `hover:shadow-*`, or `hover:-translate-y-0.5`. These are explicitly against the research findings.
